title: TRUMPTON EPISODE 3
description:
Episode 3. Mrs.Cobbit & the Ice Cream Man

One day Mrs.Cobbit fails to turn up.No flowers ! General consternation.A tree branch has crashed through her roof. Unhurt,she cleans up and gets to the Square late only to find Mr.Antonio has unwittingly taken her pitch.The happy resolution is that the fire brigade remove the branch,the Mintons repair the rafters,Antonio re-plasters the ceiling and Mrs.C sells his ice cream while he does.
